{"tid":2137440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"駐南蘇丹中方維和人員被批棄營逃跑","createTime":"2020-08-03T02:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T06:24:00.000Z","uid":6497,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fcfe3f19392465b5c749fa3780761990a7f600c6","tid":2137440,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=196355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D196355&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=3db69a8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D196355&h=6a21779f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=196355</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】聯合國駐南蘇丹的維持和平部隊人員被指在衝突中袖手旁觀，當中包括中方的維和人員，中方指有關指控是惡意炒作。<br />\n<br />\n南蘇丹的敵對派系持續衝突，今年七月，在首都朱巴的聯合國營地亦遇襲，造成兩名中國維和人員死亡。<br />\n<br />\n有人權組織日前發表報告，批評維和部隊在衝突中，沒向平民提供保護，對於有平民被殺，甚至遭性侵，視而不見。<br />\n<br />\n報告更提到中方的維和人員棄守崗位，留下彈藥和武器，逃去聯合國的主營區，有違部隊維持和平的宗旨。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，國防部發言人反駁報告的指控不實，純屬惡意炒作，強調中國維和部隊官兵當時堅守崗位，又稱聯合國正調查部隊當時的表現，指在結果公布前，任何對維和行動及人員的莫須有的指摘都是不負責任。"},{"pid":"3f07e40742c159185bf0d7c138cc650a0a526cd9","tid":2137440,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684fcc796698e7839b7f1c947dc0e5228f412f39","tid":2137440,"uid":181789,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"係都要人出埋片先收聲"},{"pid":"927aa73a6c72ec3aa1e0375419d44db00e41ded4","tid":2137440,"uid":50386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"2016年"},{"pid":"980d9becee07b1ff3d353341ce36b354343b53f8","tid":2137440,"uid":278881,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:56:01.000Z","msg":"不嬲話解放軍紙老虎<br />\n零戰鬥力<br />\n打下手無寸鐵平民就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04bc696e5d34519f84841378667affe1bc9064a","tid":2137440,"uid":335434,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"fake news 中国解放軍部隊訓練有素不知幾勇猛 又點會棄營逃跑呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58hq9bP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58hq9bP.gif&h=ecc445d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25ff56c96832f8010c42c560baa256f3e6f58919","tid":2137440,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"有冇英文"},{"pid":"554826626eaebfd7af0d9313d6dfc8b1faaba809","tid":2137440,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人權組織日前發表報告，批評維和部隊在衝突中，沒向平民提供保護，對於有平民被殺，甚至遭性侵，視而不見。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁似香港既？"},{"pid":"1535cf3e3044be1429fda73c06074faacb97f30d","tid":2137440,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:04:45.000Z","msg":"解放軍：冇油水抽，不了"},{"pid":"a4f1b33c37f32877b88829c78cc946c6b15d1025","tid":2137440,"uid":345502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a04bc696e5d34519f84841378667affe1bc9064a","tid":2137440,"uid":335434,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"fake news 中国解放軍部隊訓練有素不知幾勇猛 又點會棄營逃跑呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58hq9bP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58hq9bP.gif&h=ecc445d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:17:14.000Z","msg":"睇呢D我不如睇blackpink好過喇"},{"pid":"a5acb09d3af823d90db5488defaad0dfb207176d","tid":2137440,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04bc696e5d34519f84841378667affe1bc9064a","tid":2137440,"uid":335434,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"reply